  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Crovanta Partners ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect information when you visit crovantapartner.com or interact with our services.</p>
    <p>By using our website or engaging with our services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Information you provide directly:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, company name, and email address when you book a discovery call via Calendly</li>
      <li>Name, company, email, and the challenge you share when you interact with Vera, our AI agent</li>
      <li>Any information you provide when you email us at sanddeep@crovantapartner.com</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Information collected automatically:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Website usage data via Google Analytics — pages visited, time on site, traffic source, device type, approximate location</li>
      <li>Search performance data via Google Search Console — queries, impressions, clicks</li>
      <li>Technical data such as browser type, IP address, and referring URL</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to enquiries and schedule discovery calls</li>
      <li>To understand the challenges that brought you to us</li>
      <li>To improve our website content and user experience</li>
      <li>To understand how visitors find and use our website</li>
      <li>To send relevant communications if you have engaged with us directly</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — tracks website traffic. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Google Search Console</strong> — monitors search performance. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Calendly</strong> — manages discovery call bookings. <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank">Calendly Privacy Policy</a></li>
